1. Please run the command to install the required packages:

pip install -r requirements.txt

2. Please run the command to start the application from app.py

streamlit run app.py

Once you will run this command it will open the browser with the application.

# 3. Please upload the PDF file and click on the "Process PDF" button to process the PDF file.

# 4. After processing the PDF, you can ask questions related to the content of the PDF.

# 5. The application will return the answer to your question based on the content of the PDF.

# 6. You can ask multiple questions and the application will return the answers based on the content of the PDF.

# 7. You can also reset the application by clicking on the "Reset" button.

# 8. The application will also display the PDF file name and the number of pages in the PDF file.

# 9. The application will also display the number of documents in the knowledge base.

# 10. The application will also display the number of questions asked and the number of answers returned.

# 11. The application will also display the number of documents in the knowledge base.
